    <string name="time_based_reminder_help">Set specific times (e.g., 8:00 AM) and configure a recurring pattern. This allows precise control over specific weekdays, days of the month, or complex periodic schedules (like \'every 3 days\').</string>
    <string name="weekday_limited">Limited to some weekdays</string>
    <string name="windowed_interval_reminder">Windowed interval reminder</string>
    <string name="windowed_interval_reminder_help">Define a daily active window (e.g., 9:00 AM to 9:00 PM) where the first reminder is always at the start time. Subsequent reminders fire at fixed intervals until the end time is reached. The full pattern resets every day.</string>
